The DC Studios Showcase Podcast closes out its 2025 episodes with an explosive deep dive into the Peacemaker Season 2 finale! Join hosts Frankey Smith, Tyler Coates, and comic correspondent Coy Jandreau as they unpack one of the most talked-about DC episodes yet--packed with shocking twists, emotional character arcs, and game-changing reveals for the future of the DC Universe. 

From Chris Smith’s powerful journey to the sinister transformation of Rick Flag Sr., the hosts break down the biggest moments that left fans buzzing. Plus, the team shares personal highlights from the podcast thus far including their favorite interviews with creators and actors, and what they’ve learned along the way. 

Looking ahead, Frankey, Tyler, and Coy discuss their bold wishes for Peacemaker Season 3--from dream guest stars to epic story arcs--while teasing what’s next for DC fans with updates on Supergirl, Lanterns, and the highly anticipated Man of Tomorrow.

description:
Get ready for the ultimate Peacemaker Season 2 finale breakdown with host James Gunn and co-hosts Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt) and Steve Agee (John Economos). In this jam-packed episode of Peacemaker: The Official Podcast, the team dives deep into the iconic Season 2 finale, ‘Full Nelson’, exploring everything from the legendary party boat scene to the intricate character dynamics that make this show unforgettable. 

Hear great on-set stories, improvised lines, and insider details about how real-life connections shaped the script. Plus, discover how the cast prepares for intense fight scenes, what went into choosing standout music from Steel Panther to Nelson, and special surprises from guest appearances you won’t want to miss. 

Whether you’re a die-hard Peacemaker fan, a DC Universe enthusiast, or just love behind-the-scenes Hollywood insights, this episode delivers laughs, drama, and insider secrets.
